'''Adem Arous''' ({{langx|ar|آدم عروس}}; born 17 July 2004) is a Tunisian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[Süper Lig]] club [[Kasımpaşa S.K.|Kasımpaşa]] and the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]].

==Club career==
Arous began his senior career with [[Stade Tunisien]] in 2022, and was promoted to their senior team in 2024. On 24 January 2025, he extended his contract with Stade Tunisian until 2029.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://diwanfm.net/news/%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D9%88%D9%86%D8%B3%D9%8A-%D9%8A%D8%AC%D8%AF%D8%AF-%D8%B9%D9%82%D8%AF-%D9%85%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%B9%D9%87-%D8%A2%D8%AF%D9%85-%D8%B9%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B3%C2%A0|title=Radio Tunisie &#124;  Sfax - Radio Diwan FM - الملعب التونسي يجدد عقد مدافعه آدم عروس}}</ref> On 2 September 2025, he transferred to the Turkish [[Süper Lig]] club [[Kasımpaşa S.K.|Kasımpaşa]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://africafoot.com/kasimpasa-soffre-la-pepite-defensive-tunisienne-adem-arous/|title=Kasımpaşa s'offre la pépite défensive tunisienne Adem Arous|first=L'équipe|last=Africafoot|date=2 September 2025}}</ref>

==International career==
Arous was called up to the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]] for the [[2025 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite news |title=List of our national team for the African Cup of Nations – from 21 December 2025 to 18 January 2026 |url=https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=122162936504793506&set=pcb.122162936534793506&locale=en_GB |access-date=11 December 2025 |work=Équipe Nationale Tunisienne |publisher=Facebook |date=11 December 2025}}</ref>

